
Parallella Platform HDL Source Code and Reference Design Package
-----------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains the HDL source code of the Parallella platform and
all the data needed for the reference design implementation, described
in the "Parallella Platform Reference Design" user guide.

Following is a short description of the files and directories found under the 
root directory of this project:

README   - short package introductory file
COPYING  - GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE file
doc/     - documentation directory
hdl/     - HDL source code
hdl_top/ - Top level HDL files*
data/    - UCF files
ip/      - XCO files

*Note:
The files found under hdl_top/ sub-directory are the top level design files of 
the various Parallella platfrom versions, supported by the HDL source code in
this package. The following versions of the platform are currently supported:

- Parallella-16 Prototype (ZedBoard and 16-core Epiphany FMC)
- Parallella-64 Prototype (ZedBoard and 64-core Epiphany FMC)

